@Node "About the playing routine"

   The computer player is based on a algorithm made by
   @{" Magnus " Link "Magnus" } Enarsson (me). The routine is very optimized to
   be fast, but it doesn't play that well. I have some ideas
   of how to make it very hard to beat but I keep them to
   further releases (if any). Still Luffar is good enough
   to entertain most people.
   Mail me and let me know what YOU think.

@EndNode


